00:35:38.640 --> 00:35:42.687
<v Adam> You know, I don't remember off the top of my head. 

521
00:35:42.687 --> 00:35:45.914
It is probably a very broad license. 

522
00:35:45.914 --> 00:35:54.262
I mean, basically we looked at the websites that we had 

